rows.label: qst201616_0010
rows.name: Kiara...

rows.label: qst201616_0020
rows.name: That went great!

rows.label: qst201616_0030
rows.name:
Yeah!
It was awesome!

rows.label: qst201616_0040
rows.name:
You could really see how much
you were enjoying yourself there!

rows.label: qst201616_0050
rows.name:
Everyone really loved you! There were butterflies in our
stomachs! And flapping birds in our hearts!

rows.label: qst201616_0060
rows.name: It's all thanks to you, Kiara!

rows.label: qst201616_0070
rows.name:
You spoke to me... If you hadn't have spoken to me
that time, none of this would have happened.

rows.label: qst201616_0080
rows.name:
Kiara, I've played the Torigonda
that you lent me so much...

rows.label: qst201616_0090
rows.name:
I said I'd give it back to you...
I made that promise when we first met.

rows.label: qst201616_0100
rows.name: Perhaps...now is the time for me to return it.

rows.label: qst201616_0110
rows.name: No...

rows.label: qst201616_0120
rows.name: I want you to keep the Torigonda.

rows.label: qst201616_0130
rows.name:
I mean...
Da can always make another one.

rows.label: qst201616_0140
rows.name:
Today feels like...
A graduation ceremony of sorts.

rows.label: qst201616_0150
rows.name:
I wanted to give a once-in-a-lifetime
performance...and I think I did.

rows.label: qst201616_0160
rows.name: Mo-mo-moooo?!

rows.label: qst201616_0170
rows.name: Really?

rows.label: qst201616_0180
rows.name:
I've always wanted to be brave in battle...
To do my best for the sake of my friends...

rows.label: qst201616_0190
rows.name: I've had these thoughts since the start...

rows.label: qst201616_0200
rows.name: But out there, on stage...

rows.label: qst201616_0210
rows.name:
With so many people listening
to me, to my song...

rows.label: qst201616_0220
rows.name:
I finally felt complete, whole.
Ready to move on.

rows.label: qst201616_0230
rows.name: Mo!! Mo-mo...

rows.label: qst201616_0240
rows.name: That's incredible.

rows.label: qst201616_0250
rows.name: I'd be sad to think I'll never hear you sing again...

rows.label: qst201616_0260
rows.name:
I bet everyone who came here today
would be gutted, too.

rows.label: qst201616_0280
rows.name: But, it's up to you, of course!

rows.label: qst201616_0290
rows.name:
I'm sure you'll do great things,
whether as a fighter, or musician.

rows.label: qst201616_0300
rows.name: Yes! I promise to make you proud!

rows.label: qst201616_0310
rows.name: But I had so much help from the Drivers and Producer...

rows.label: qst201616_0320
rows.name: Now it's my turn to give something back!

rows.label: qst201616_0330
rows.name: That's the spirit!

rows.label: qst201616_0360
rows.name: Thanks for everything!

rows.label: qst201616_0370
rows.name: You really are welcome!
